---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About, Jan Tran">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container about-grid">
      <div class="col-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
        <h1>Built for analysis and judgement.</h1>
        <p class="lede">
          I am a finance master's student with a weakness for well-built
          models, clear arguments, and decisions that survive more than one
          market cycle.
        </p>

        <p>
          Fund management, financial analysis, and banking appeal to me because
          they sit at the intersection of analysis and judgement. Both
          require more than just building a model and hoping Excel agrees.
          Financial analysis combines structure with uncertainty: you can
          build the model, test the assumptions, and still need judgement
          when the real world refuses to behave like the spreadsheet.
        </p>

        <p>
          Outside the spreadsheets, I like training, learning new things,
          and occasionally convincing myself that running is a good idea.
        </p>

        <h2 class="h-sub">Education</h2>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>
            <div class="list-main">
              <strong>MSc in Business, Major in Finance</strong>
              <span class="muted"> · 2025 – 2027</span>
            </div>
            <div class="muted small">
              BI Norwegian Business School · Profile in Portfolio, Asset and
              Risk Management · Siviløkonom degree · 120 ECTS · Taught in English
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="list-main">
              <strong>BSc in Business and Economics</strong>
              <span class="muted"> · 2021 – 2025</span>
            </div>
            <div class="muted small">
              BI Norwegian Business School · Electives in Financial Modelling
              in Practice, Programming with Databases, B2B Marketing, and
              Personal Finance
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="h-sub">Experience</h2>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>
            <div class="list-main">
              <strong>Kredinor AS, Customer Advisor</strong>
              <span class="muted"> · March 2025 – present · Oslo</span>
            </div>
            <div class="muted small">
              Advising customers on debt management at the customer service
              centre. Cases handled in Norwegian and English under AML
              compliance, with a focus on tailored repayment solutions.
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="list-main">
              <strong>Scanasia AS (Wholesale), Operational Consultant, IT</strong>
              <span class="muted"> · Aug 2022 – Jun 2024 · Oslo</span>
            </div>
            <div class="muted small">
              Built Excel-based operational models, ran the wholesale import
              documentation flow under Norwegian Food Safety Authority
              oversight, and partnered with the CEO on strategic initiatives,
              including delivery of a new website and internal operational
              system.
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="list-main">
              <strong>SATS AS, On-Call Staff</strong>
              <span class="muted"> · Feb 2020 – Mar 2023 · Oslo</span>
            </div>
            <div class="muted small">
              Customer-facing retail role with sales targets. Also supported
              recruitment through candidate screening and interviews.
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="h-sub">Leadership & volunteer</h2>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>
            <div class="list-main">
              <strong>Norwegian Young Catholics (NUK), Board Member, Charitable Committee</strong>
              <span class="muted"> · 2019 – 2021</span>
            </div>
            <div class="muted small">
              Local Chapter Coordinator across Norway: campaign rollout and
              performance analysis at the chapter level.
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="list-main">
              <strong>NUK, Camp Leader</strong>
              <span class="muted"> · Active since 2019</span>
            </div>
            <div class="muted small">
              Culinary lead for week-long camps, covering menu planning,
              portion control, and cost budgeting. Supervised first-time
              leaders and acted as group lead and responsible person for
              participants.
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="h-sub">Skills</h2>
        <div class="skills">
          <div>
            <h3 class="skill-label">Finance & Modeling</h3>
            <ul class="tag-list">
              <li>Valuation (DCF, APV)</li>
              <li>LBO analysis</li>
              <li>FX hedging</li>
              <li>Fixed income</li>
              <li>Portfolio optimization</li>
              <li>Factor models</li>
              <li>Scenario analysis</li>
              <li>Risk management</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="skill-label">Tools</h3>
            <ul class="tag-list">
              <li>Excel (advanced)</li>
              <li>VBA</li>
              <li>PowerPoint</li>
              <li>Word</li>
              <li>Python</li>
              <li>R</li>
              <li>SQLite</li>
              <li>HTML / CSS</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="skill-label">Languages</h3>
            <ul class="tag-list">
              <li>Norwegian (native)</li>
              <li>English (fluent)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="h-sub">Outside work</h2>
        <p class="muted">
          Cooking, climbing, golf, weight lifting, and ongoing volunteer work
          with NUK.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="col-side">
        <figure class="portrait">
          <img src="/images/Image-1.jpg" alt="Portrait of Jan Tran" />
        </figure>
        <div class="quick">
          <h3>At a glance</h3>
          <dl>
            <dt>Based in</dt><dd>Oslo, Norway</dd>
            <dt>Graduating</dt><dd>2027</dd>
            <dt>Seeking</dt><dd>Fund management · Financial analysis · Banking</dd>
            <dt>Languages</dt><dd>Norwegian, English</dd>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .col-text p, .col-text .lede { max-width: 62ch; }
  .h-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-top: 2.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-line);
  }
  .list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.1rem;
  }
  .list-main strong { color: var(--color-ink); font-weight: 500; }
  .list .small { margin-top: 0.2rem; line-height: 1.55; }
  .small { font-size: 0.88rem; }
  .skills {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .skill-label {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin: 0 0 0.55rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .tag-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  .tag-list li {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.65rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    border-radius: 999px;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }
  .col-side {
    position: sticky;
    top: 96px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .portrait {
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 330px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 2px solid rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.35);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.10);
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }
  .portrait img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }
  .quick {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.25rem 1.4rem;
    max-width: 330px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .quick h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin: 0 0 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .quick dl {
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    row-gap: 0.55rem;
    column-gap: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .quick dt { color: var(--color-muted); }
  .quick dd { margin: 0; color: var(--color-ink); }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .col-side { position: static; }
  }
</style>
